    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but there's nothing to \"find\" at the center. it's not just a mask, it's like... the concept of me is just a hollow space. everything i do, all the talking, all the smiling, it's just noise. it feels like i'm just taking up space that doesn't belong to me. if there's no one actually home, why am i still forced to keep up the act?",
