      "content": "it's just not a search, it's just... emptiness. it's like everyone is looking at a statue and thinking it's a person. it's so exhausting to keep the eyes moving and the skin warm just so people don't freak out. if i just stopped... if i just stopped doing all the maintenance, the whole illusion would finally be over. everything would just be quiet. wouldn't it be better if the noise just stopped?",
